{"tid":1171353,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"喺2047年嘅時候，你唔會再記得我","createTime":"2019-05-25T15:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T20:19:01.000Z","uid":200120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b56e04e191fd73e38c560f6631dbbeb231bd6870","tid":1171353,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"二十八年後嘅今日，你已經忘記咗我<br />\n因為由今日開始，我決定唔再搵你<br />\n<br />\n但喺2047嘅時候，我依然記得你<br />\n因為我每日都在想你<br />\n<br />\n或者我唔應該咁快下結論<br />\n等六月九日去拋一個命運硬幣<br />\n<br />\n我知勇氣係無用<br />\n但我只得勇氣作最後的籌碼<br />\n<br />\n致我愛的你<br />\n和<br />\n我愛的香港"},{"pid":"9e720f8757a0014acea9d4c80b65d5bc2b81d955","tid":1171353,"uid":240150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T20:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}